{"tid":2334711,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸IT員工猝死半小時被發現　網民熱議：「996」工作制惹的禍","createTime":"2020-12-21T10:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T11:37:03.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7233014c2269f076ed5e8aa78a0be5886b0a5e","tid":2334711,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n人工智能平台公司商湯科技上周六（19日）證實一名47歲員工在公司猝死，相關影片也在網上流傳，更有指這名男子暈倒半小時後才被同事發現報案，救護員到場時證實他已猝逝。熱烈討論事件的內地網民，聯想起內地科技界近年流傳「996」（朝9晚9，每周上班6日）工作制、「007」（朝0晚24，每周上班7日）工作制，甚至指如果加班納入《刑法》的一天來到，「公司一定不是無辜。」<br />\n從流傳影片見，一名身穿黑色運動衣服的男子，身體僵直地靠在椅上，臉部朝上，手臂捲曲，小腿位置有明顯瘀傷，手機掉落在腳邊。商湯科技官方微博回應事件時稱，「商湯公司第一時間向其家人和親屬通報情況，同時積極配合警方調查。商湯一直非常重視員工健康，已全力協助親屬妥善安排後事並撫恤。願逝者安息！」<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201221/S7I6ZAIK7FDFXES4K27ORMMFTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201221%2FS7I6ZAIK7FDFXES4K27ORMMFTA%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=907bd886\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201221%2FS7I6ZAIK7FDFXES4K27ORMMFTA%2F&h=79eb417c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201221/S7I6ZAIK7FDFXES4K27ORMMFTA/</a>"},{"pid":"e28ffe8a72f5379d78aa576b6bac11d4fc29c609","tid":2334711,"uid":98899,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:58:23.000Z","msg":"007係咩玩法<br />\n唔洗訓唔洗沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149e065fe14b65c89de137afdfcd8d17f6e21c99","tid":2334711,"uid":78336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"抵啦 整監控 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5620ea515db3e98291dc60254d5ebbfed8610d7a","tid":2334711,"uid":53126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:09:11.000Z","msg":"爆肝工程師的異世界狂想曲<img src=\"/assets/fa